# Talent and Content Management System

ERP/CMC System, covering the tasks and work scenarios of a Musical Label, a Talent Agency or a Publishing, connecting together and keeping up-to-date all Content (Tracks, Albums, Videos, Images etc.), Copyright Information, Financial Data and more.

Easily organizes the chaos of documents, media and transactions into an easily accessible data structure. Handy apps help to import and parse data, export reports and analyse statistics.
